Treat is a responsive cloud-based software (designed for restaurants) for billing, accounting (Tax/GST calculation) and inventory management with the proper dashboard (sales, expenses, and low inventory reporting system).
Other features:
1. jQuery-AJAX Live (keyup) Search for faster billing.
2. Multiple-table billing at the same time.
3. Staff management system for keeping salary, attendance, and other records.
Technologies used: PHP, MySQL, Bootstrap, Javascript, AJAX, jQuery, LAMP.
